{"tid":2264354,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男女校奇聞","createTime":"2020-10-30T14:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:11:23.000Z","uid":375316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7f467e345f1c50de797199944b4921b2d68372","tid":2264354,"uid":375316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"見到嗰個讀女校通病<br />\n搞到我都想講吓男女校<br />\n男女校好容易有審美疲勞<br />\n望內左會覺得其實間學校啲仔唔差<br />\n都可以接受到 <br />\n但係其實全部都係肥矮毒柒<br />\n一係就係死狗公 以為自己好型嘅死mk<br />\n真係正常樣嘅 真係五隻手指數得晒<br />\n然後就係好多換妻派對<br />\n呢個星期見到男A同女B一齊左<br />\n可能下個月女B就同左男A個frd一齊<br />\n再下個月男A又同女B嗰好姊妹一齊<br />\n可能佢嗰班小圈子有七男七女<br />\n然後個7pair係可以每個月都唔同<br />\n然後佢哋成班圍內係竟然唔介意<br />\n唔知係咪得我間學校係咁撚奇怪"},{"pid":"0875e72057c776b7795768b58e6238d3268812f8","tid":2264354,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"做晒功課未啊"},{"pid":"0212dace9e92e268b563f9713a7d29eb7f4cea76","tid":2264354,"uid":369015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔同意，之前望耐咗都覺學校啲女柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfcbf89c9ff33b003627f4c20944cb79240abba","tid":2264354,"uid":375316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0875e72057c776b7795768b58e6238d3268812f8","tid":2264354,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"做晒功課未啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"畢咗業啦"},{"pid":"c6d5c37faa8689368e1217ab9a37edb5de73ded4","tid":2264354,"uid":375316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0212dace9e92e268b563f9713a7d29eb7f4cea76","tid":2264354,"uid":369015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔同意，之前望耐咗都覺學校啲女柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"咁可能你嗰間啲女係真係唔多掂"}]}